---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About - May">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>About me</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="content narrow">
    <p class="lead">
      You can call me May. I work with technology, product, and people - and I think way too much about how we should live our lives and make decisions.
    </p>

    <p>
      I've always built things. An urban mobility startup in college, a jewelry ecommerce with my family, and even decision support systems using optimization algorithms for oil well drilling (yeah, quite the mix). I joined Stone when we had fewer than 50,000 customers — today that's less than what we onboard in a month. I left briefly to lead the financial services front at a software startup, and when I came back it was to help build the people team during a phase of insane growth. I watched the company go from 6,000 to 15,000 people, lose nearly 80% of its market cap, and rebuild itself. All from backstage.
    </p>

    <p>
      I went back to my roots - product and artificial intelligence (except in 2014 we didn't call it that). Today I lead our commercial platform's AI-first transformation and build AI products for Brazilian small businesses.
    </p>

    <p class="closing">
      The resume zigzags, just like life. In every challenge I've brought to the table what I do best - systems thinking that connects technology with real problems, and the drive to make things happen.
    </p>

    <div class="divider" style="margin: 3rem auto;"></div>

    <h2>This space</h2>

    <p>
      This is my lab - a bit of work, reflections, and 100% sandbox for fun. I'm very curious and would love to collaborate with people who connect with what they find here.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you're also thinking about these things, say hi: <a href="mailto:hello@mayra.villas">hello@mayra.villas</a>
    </p>

    <p>
      I don't have social media other than <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mayravillasboas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 5rem auto 3rem;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
  }

  .content {
    padding: 0 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .closing {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
